######################
>> No Pre-Processing
######################
>> input:
    - sentece
    - dataset: sentence list

>> create feature matrix
    - calculate ngrams for each word
    - get set(all anagrams in the data given)
    - calculate TF-IDF matrix

>> calculate similarity
    - dot product
        - input sentence feature vector (1xN)
        - dataset feature matrix (MxN)
        - parameters
            - M: length of dataset
            - N: number of unique anagrams in all given data